If you sign a contract with me,

36
00:03:13,370 --> 00:03:14,720
I'll give you the title.

37
00:03:18,550 --> 00:03:19,660
So if

38
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,210
you figure out,

39
00:03:21,370 --> 00:03:22,960
