They are sure to have
a good result in a year.

81
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:41,820
Gao Zhiyi.

82
00:04:41,909 --> 00:04:43,790
I really think there’s something
wrong with your values.

83
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:44,800
