115
00:05:54,330 --> 00:05:56,340
One to one?

116
00:05:56,510 --> 00:05:57,680
Please.

117
00:06:00,030 --> 00:06:01,300
Great view.

118
00:06:01,890 --> 00:06:03,490
If I could smoke,

119
