164
00:07:48,790 --> 00:07:50,420
Hi, where do I put your bed?

165
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:52,409
Please put it in the study.

166
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:07,730
Mr. Zhang, this bed...

167
00:08:07,820 --> 00:08:08,610
I hope

168
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:10,230
