191
00:09:12,770 --> 00:09:13,610
Mr. Zhang.

192
00:09:13,710 --> 00:09:14,940
This is the access card.

193
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,920
Now I give it back.

194
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:18,900
Well.

195
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,770
Mr. Zhang, Mr. Zhang.

196
00:09:46,810 --> 00:09:47,410
Mr. Zhang.

197
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:48,950
