Sister.

201
00:09:54,530 --> 00:09:55,020
Sister?

202
00:09:55,190 --> 00:09:56,380
What are you up to here?

203
00:09:56,470 --> 00:09:57,620
Sis, why are you back?

204
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,740
I'll take the case.

205
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:00,820
Shouldn't I be back?

206
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:03,240
