276
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:09,910
Really?

277
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:10,540
Yes.

278
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:11,850
How did you fall in love?

279
00:14:12,110 --> 00:14:13,570
It is because...

280
00:14:14,400 --> 00:14:15,280
of the house.

281
00:14:15,370 --> 00:14:16,610
